  "body_text": null,
  "page": null,
  "source": "[a \\.minimal.in./ X]\nStates:\nwhen:\n. a is \\set\n. X is \\set\nthat:\n. forAll: x is \\set\n  where:\n  . x \"in\" X\n  then:\n  . if:\n    . x \\:precedes:/ a\n    then:\n    . x = a\nDocumented:\n. called: \"minimal element\"\n. written: \"a? \\text{ is minimal in } X?\"\n. description: \"An element $a$ is minimal in $X$ when $x \\preceq a$ implies $x = a$ for all $x \\in X$; equivalently, no element strictly precedes $a$.\"\nId: \"524c9a41-1363-4170-9dab-6eb99f2cf373\"",
